1 43.050. 1. The superintendent may appoint not more
2 than thirty-four captains and one director of radio, each of
3 whom shall have the same qualifications as the
4 superintendent, nor more than sixty-eight lieutenants, and
5 such additional force of sergeants, corporals and patrolmen,
6 so that the total number of members of the patrol shall not
7 exceed one thousand sixty-four officers and patrolmen and
